{"tid":700750,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"（集思廣益）單身窮毒撚餐單 ：一星期為單位","createTime":"2018-06-13T14:56:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T05:13:59.000Z","uid":29041,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5367b98e246ec18215c6629ca0e198cbba1b963c","tid":700750,"uid":29041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T14:56:38.000Z","msg":"假設70kg 成年男人<br />\n<br />\n要求：<br />\n<br />\n食材平 :平均10～20一餐<br />\n食材擺得耐，唔洗點雪：可以擺一個星期以上<br />\n健康 營養均衡<br />\n容易煮<br />\n<br />\n餐單：<br />\n早餐：即食燕麥 ，常溫牛奶/豆奶<br />\n午餐：雜豆通粉，水煮蛋<br />\n晚餐：雜豆通粉 ，橙<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲一齊諗個餐單"},{"pid":"3d608a741edaa7bba2b3f133e3eac7378232da89","tid":700750,"uid":49730,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T14:58:24.000Z","msg":"大快活"},{"pid":"90cfc9d8b91c73ee639fc3e0bee7015e92af64e7","tid":700750,"uid":29041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d608a741edaa7bba2b3f133e3eac7378232da89","tid":700750,"uid":49730,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T14:58:24.000Z","msg":"大快活"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T15:03:49.000Z","msg":"貴過20$"},{"pid":"fa55569be3263cdbfeb7d527161c9f0dcff4552b","tid":700750,"uid":29041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T00:15:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f5a452181f89ee403517ad003e79ba66440bf50a","tid":700750,"uid":18117,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T01:26:14.000Z","msg":"煎豆腐 買幾蚊食到你嘔<br />\n鯪魚肉 買十蚊分兩餐食 淥又得炒菜又得 煎魚餅都得<br />\n想有啲變化咪撈啲豬肉碎做鯪魚肉餅 豬肉釀豆腐又得<br />\n清清地就生菜豆腐鯪魚肉滾個湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1c7de0655a2d138551dbe2b8b98751bbe9f3513","tid":700750,"uid":18117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5a452181f89ee403517ad003e79ba66440bf50a","tid":700750,"uid":18117,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T01:26:14.000Z","msg":"煎豆腐 買幾蚊食到你嘔<br />\n鯪魚肉 買十蚊分兩餐食 淥又得炒菜又得 煎魚餅都得<br />\n想有啲變化咪撈啲豬肉碎做鯪魚肉餅 豬肉釀豆腐又得<br />\n清清地就生菜豆腐鯪魚肉滾個湯<img sr